1 H.461
2 An act relating to expanding employee access to unpaid leave
3 The Senate proposes to the House to amend the bill by striking out all after
4 the enacting clause and inserting in lieu thereof the following:
5 Sec. 1. INTENT
6 It is the intent of the General Assembly to align Vermont’s family leave
7 policies with inclusive and equitable standards, ensuring that LGBTQ+
8 families, workers with low income, and individuals in nontraditional family
9 structures have equal access to caregiving leave without undue burden.
